data.name: Dui, the Invaluable
data.notes: "Dui, the Invaluable" is in the north west most corner of the devils colony cave system which can be entered a short ways east of Oblivia Ingress at the north end of Yawning Giant. At each junction go north, east, north and then west down the long tunnel to find Dui, the Invaluable crawling in a small pool of water at the end.
